Liminal MX is a Mexican DJ and producer who weaves a unique sonic narrative through his mixes and productions, combining the best of House with deep melodies and melancholic harmonies. With a focus on emotion, his sets stand out for their seamless fusion of immersive beats and R&B-inspired vocals, creating an atmosphere that is both introspective and vibrant.

Liminal MX has crafted a style that navigates between the melodic and the emotional, immersing his audience in a musical experience that explores the boundaries between the dance floor and introspection.
